<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

<title>RLT Music and Filmworks</title>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box
}

body{
    background:#000;
    color:white;
    font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

a{
    text-decoration:none;
    color:white;
}

.hero{
    width:100%;
    min-height:100vh;
    background:url('/rlt-homepage.png') center top/cover no-repeat;
    position:relative;
}

.overlay{
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.55);
    width:100%;
    min-height:100vh;
}

.navbar{
    width:100%;
    padding:25px 60px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    position:fixed;
    top:0;
    z-index:1000;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,.75);
    backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#f3c64d;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
}

.nav-links{
    display:flex;
    gap:35px;
}

.nav-links a{
    font-size:14px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    transition:.3s;
}

.nav-links a:hover{
    color:#f3c64d;
}

.hero-content{
    width:100%;
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:120px 20px 60px;
}

.hero-box{
    max-width:900px;
}

.hero-box h1{
    font-size:82px;
    line-height:1;
    font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    color:#f3c64d;
    text-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(243,198,77,.4);
}

.hero-box p{
    font-size:20px;
    line-height:1.8;
    margin-bottom:40px;
    color:#e0e0e0;
}

.hero-buttons{
    display:flex;
    gap:20px;
    justify-content:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.btn{
    padding:16px 34px;
    border:2px solid #f3c64d;
    color:#f3c64d;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    font-weight:600;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#f3c64d;
    color:black;
}

.section{
    padding:100px 60px;
    background:black;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:52px;
    margin-bottom:60px;
    color:#f3c64d;
    font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
    text-transform:uppercase;
}

.cards{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
    gap:30px;
}

.card{
    background:#0c0c0c;
    border:1px solid #1f1f1f;
    overflow:hidden;
    transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
    border-color:#f3c64d;
}

.card img{
    width:100%;
    height:260px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.card-content{
    padding:30px;
}

.card-content h3{
    font-size:30px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    color:#f3c64d;
    font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
}

.card-content p{
    line-height:1.8;
    color:#d0d0d0;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.footer{
    background:#050505;
    padding:60px 30px;
    text-align:center;
    border-top:1px solid #111;
}

.footer h2{
    color:#f3c64d;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;
}

.footer p{
    color:#bdbdbd;
    line-height:1.8;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

    .navbar{
        flex-direction:column;
        gap:20px;
        padding:20px;
    }

    .nav-links{
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        justify-content:center;
        gap:20px;
    }

    .hero-box h1{
        font-size:48px;
    }

    .hero-box p{
        font-size:16px;
    }

    .section{
        padding:80px 25px;
    }

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<section class="hero">

<div class="overlay">

<nav class="navbar">

<div class="logo">
RLT MUSIC &amp; FILMWORKS
</div>

<div class="nav-links">
<a href="/">Home</a>
<a href="/music">Music</a>
<a href="/film">Film</a>
<a href="/store">Store</a>
<a href="/artists">Artists</a>
<a href="/ozone">Ozone</a>
<a href="/contact">Contact</a>
</div>

</nav>

<div class="hero-content">

<div class="hero-box">

<h1>
Real Music.<br>
Real Stories.<br>
Real Impact.
</h1>

<p>
Music • Film • Culture • Legacy
</p>

<div class="hero-buttons">
<a href="/music" class="btn">Explore Music</a>
<a href="/film" class="btn">View Films</a>
</div>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<h2 class="section-title">
Our Divisions
</h2>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<img src="/rlt-homepage.png" alt="">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Music Division</h3>
<p>
From timeless classics to the next generation of hits, RLT continues building a legacy through sound.
</p>
<a href="/music" class="btn">Explore</a>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="/rlt-homepage.png" alt="">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Film Works</h3>
<p>
Original documentaries, visual storytelling, and cinematic productions that inspire culture and creativity.
</p>
<a href="/film" class="btn">View Films</a>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="/rlt-homepage.png" alt="">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>The Store</h3>
<p>
Official merchandise, collectibles, music releases, and exclusive RLT branded products.
</p>
<a href="/store" class="btn">Shop Now</a>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer class="footer">

<h2>RLT Music and Filmworks</h2>

<p>
10134 6th Street Suite H<br>
Rancho Cucamonga, CA 91730<br>
Tel: (219) 201-6827
</p>

<br>

<p>
© 2026 RLT Music and Filmworks. All Rights Reserved.
</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
